{"tid":1414095,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"警向記者大叫「影乜野呀」 隨即向記者方向施放催淚彈","createTime":"2019-08-05T11:41:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-05T12:04:31.000Z","uid":212626,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"1a1968489e400059ddac51f90806c5dc1dd6c085","tid":1414095,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T11:41:34.000Z","msg":"反修例行動持續，民間發動今日（5日）「全港三罷」（罷工、罷課、罷市），並在7區集會，其後多區爆發多次警民衝突，警方多次施放催淚彈驅趕市示威者，不過TOPick發現警方不時都在高處向地面發射催淚彈，甚至射向行人天橋上。<br />\n<br />\n在金鐘添馬公園的集會，亦有集會人士衝出金鐘夏愨道，佔據來回東西行，防暴警其後發射催淚彈，驅趕夏愨道的示威者，其中有警員多次從海富天橋連接政總的公園，向海富天橋和夏愨道，發射催淚彈。<span style=\"color: red;\">亦有防暴警在金鐘海富天橋，向記者大叫「影乜野呀」，隨即在水馬縫中，向多名正在拍攝的記者，施放胡椒噴劑及催淚彈。</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://topick.hket.com/article/2419502/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2419502%2F&d=vE0XmFSztYUmu7sR0UJCJNnRRycoFBIefads3zMUO1U%3D&h=5c6a6b0d\" target=\"_blank\">https://topick.hket.com/article/2419502/</a>"},{"pid":"63cbad402a13018bd7a036c9a8f20df519276fb4","tid":1414095,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T11:44:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qoPXLhM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqoPXLhM.jpg&h=24fe9c43&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"147b0d63a69b870cfa0b9c318f9bcaa6fdf2ea21","tid":1414095,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T11:50:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7fc4a7110da22a6db23b570e5270dceaa4530152","tid":1414095,"uid":259613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T11:51:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"70731b4c418112618b0f0f6cf746af01dc06fd15","tid":141